name: Honey Stinger GF Salted Caramel Waffle
description:
The smooth sweetness of salted caramel sandwiched between 2 thin waffles and ready to provide a quick hit of carbs on a long ride. Also excellent with coffee or tea as a mid-morning snack.100% organic ingredients.140 calories per waffle.Ingredients: gluten free flour blend (rice flour, potato starch, tapioca flour), palm fruit oil, brown rice syrup, cane sugar, eggs, soy flour, sea salt, honey, natural flavor, xanthan gum, baking soda, soy lecithin .Contains: Soy and eggs.May contain milk.
